title: Udyr (Godyr) with a bit of Trick2G Thug Style

embed.description: Just trying out some new mechanics based on some Trick2G I've seen. Screw Rageblade, Trick2G thuggin' is all ya'll need, haha. His style works really well on lower tier, bronzies to silver will not know how to deal with it, too fast and too aggressive.
